Content:
FORUM HUKUM MABASED is a discussion platform that examines and analyzes positive law in Indonesia, as well as explores ideas of an ideal and future-oriented legal system. This forum brings together thinkers, students, practitioners, and the public to engage in open, critical, and academically responsible legal discussions to promote legal awareness and social justice.

Subject of Discussion:
1. Public Law (Pidana);
2. Civil Law (Perdata);
3. Administrative Law (HAN);
4. Constitutional Law (HTN);
5. Customary and Islamic Law (Adat dan Islam);
6. International Law (HI); and,
7. Legal Policy and Philosophy (Politik dan filsafat);

Base:
- UUD 1945;
- UU, PP, and etc;
- Books, doctrine, Jurispudence, etc;
- Balegnas and Prolegnas, and;
- articles and Journals;
